172bd377592aae0cb25ee7109903b207ed7fb7b7","tid":1044054,"uid":77788,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bd164f85a339f6c015079aa056d209cd847eaab0","tid":1044054,"uid":59014,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:55:01.000Z","msg":"佢可能映射緊D網紅 youtuber 拍網片既人<br />\n當有一日以上個D都可以提名既話 , 對成個電影發展都唔係好事黎<br />\n當然roma真係導演有D料到 <br />\n但steven可能想警戒一下從影既人員 拎獎提名唔係隨便一部手機 相機就做到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T19:19:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:24:08.000Z","msg":"要求喺戲院上可以確保部電影有一定水準<br />\n<br />\n單反拍攝都賺大錢既話<br />\n以後唔使花咁多心血時間拍imax、做杜比混音、專業調色<br />\n反正觀眾都係搭車用電話睇<br />\n<br />\n劇本一定會變質 回應移動平台既市場<br />\n方便你暫停做完自己嘢 繼續播放都記得返劇情<br />\n遲早變成劣幣驅逐良幣<br />\n<br />\n周邊行業生存環境只會越來越差<br />\n做唔到生意 做唔到藝術<br />\n觀眾又冇得睇好嘢<br />\n係雙輸局面<br />\nspielberg先係真正有遠見嗰個"},{"pid":"b2c22bae37644b254e39d5ab80ab1f08fba5cb4e","tid":1044054,"uid":149494,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:30:49.000Z","msg":"同意Spielberg<br />\n你老味就廢老,人地幾撚有遠見"},{"pid":"8c5a8b6bb082fd1544d8e0f5bdab4f9cb226126c","tid":1044054,"uid":33734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b644bb99527e06240fbf06ed89e0114056c6994a","tid":1044054,"uid":48479,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5558b493193dbb2ff95adbe7c01cc703ed4d27b2","tid":1044054,"uid":33734,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T16:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.empireonline.com/jpg/70/0/0/640/480/aspectfit/0/0/0/0/0/0/c/articles/5a8d86286349688f412779fe/scorsese-spielberg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.empireonline.com%2Fjpg%2F70%2F0%2F0%2F640%2F480%2Faspectfit%2F0%2F0%2F0%2F0%2F0%2F0%2Fc%2Farticles%2F5a8d86286349688f412779fe%2Fscorsese-spielberg.jpg&h=c2c5be77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇黎你個好朋友史高斯要搵你傾一傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so