真係無可以係傳統電影業入面出到世"},{"pid":"11107f8bed74e79256e50d3d1b9f937a60b5dace","tid":1044054,"uid":77788,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T07:49:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85e3d701872da513de1b95de11b8e5b670720cb3","tid":1044054,"uid":77788,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T08:00:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cde3566c88d3b87229201eabaee76baba62ee67a","tid":1044054,"uid":29336,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"11107f8bed74e79256e50d3d1b9f937a60b5dace","tid":1044054,"uid":77788,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ecfb99cb9bd147205ae3816bf303eeaea8012c3d","tid":1044054,"uid":42691,"like":16,"dislike":6,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"172bd377592aae0cb25ee7109903b207ed7fb7b7","tid":1044054,"uid":77788,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T19:19:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:24:08.000Z","msg":"要求喺戲院上可以確保部電影有一定水準<br />\n<br />\n單反拍攝都賺大錢既話<br />\n以後唔使花咁多心血時間拍imax、做杜比混音、專業調色<br />\n反正觀眾都係搭車用電話睇<br />\n<br />\n劇本一定會變質 回應移動平台既市場<br />\n方便你暫停做完自己嘢 繼續播放都記得返劇情<br />\n遲早變成劣幣驅逐良幣<br />\n<br />\n周邊行業生存環境只會越來越差<br />\n做唔到生意 做唔到藝術<br />\n觀眾又冇得睇好嘢<br />\n係雙輸局面<br />\nspielberg先係真正有遠見嗰個"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T07:49:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T08:04:36.000Z","msg":"agger <br />\n完全掉轉黎講<br />\n宜家就係乜戲都Imax打鬥英雄片大賣<br />\n周邊小品藝術片先冇得玩<br />\n宜家多個平台反而話imax 杜比冇得做"},{"pid":"a45ebab1f7a9d65febb9793fc50b809802c2d26a","tid":1044054,"uid":56302,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"85e3d701872da513de1b95de11b8e5b670720cb3","tid":1044054,"uid":77788,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d45266385defbe64433eb51a4cd589e0b959ee6f","tid":1044054,"uid":226155,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3799c271ae459441bf747974924d4959b8c586d9","tid":1044054,"uid":77788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T19:23:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime